Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.77,0:00:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier 而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.27,0:00:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.98,0:00:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角 追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.42,0:00:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.33,0:00:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.90,0:00:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.94,0:00:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.51,0:00:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.11,0:00:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.45,0:00:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.05,0:00:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.65,0:01:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.09,0:01:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.66,0:01:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.26,0:01:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.59,0:01:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.16,0:01:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.83,0:01:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.64,0:01:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.44,0:01:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.79,0:02:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在茅葺總理正握手歡迎休雷德國務卿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.39,0:02:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次大戰後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.49,0:02:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美帝以強大軍事國家之姿誇示其力量至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.46,0:02:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在隨著經濟破產所帶來的國力下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.87,0:02:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了探討日本主導下的安保再締結案的草案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.10,0:02:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急派遣國務卿到日本來表現出不顧身段的應對方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.01,0:02:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是日本政府如果看看國內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.01,0:02:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,景氣的不安定感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民對策的遲延
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及憲法第9條問題等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,9條問題：日本自詡為「和平憲法」中涉及戰爭放棄原則的第9條所引起的爭議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課題也堆積如山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.98,0:02:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來自各方面的抗議行動必定會逐漸激化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.79,0:02:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要連休息時間都看這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.39,0:02:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算輸到脫褲子也不要遷怒到別人身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒資格說我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次我贏定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.35,0:03:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,＃14  小心左眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.19,0:03:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我問你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.39,0:03:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼事到如今還要簽訂安全保障呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.07,0:03:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本不是也有軍隊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.73,0:03:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的政府雖然是超級鷹派政權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.50,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 正因為現在美帝經濟蕭條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.47,0:03:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才想在自己掌握主導權的狀態下締結安保條約啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是想洗刷前世紀的屈辱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.08,0:03:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前世紀的屈辱是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛...簡單來說就是戰敗的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.55,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上憲法第9條這個不確定的裝置目前還在運作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.55,0:03:53.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本國憲法第9條：日本國民真誠地企望以正義和秩序為基調的國際和平\N永遠放棄國家主權發動的戰爭、武力威脅或使用武力作為解決國際爭端的手段\N為達此目的，日本不保持陸海空軍和其他戰爭力量，不承認國家交戰權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.76,0:03:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自衛軍不能公開出去外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能擁有核武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.16,0:04:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然前世紀的安保是在屈辱之下達成協議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.90,0:04:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 美國當矛日本當盾的不可分默契還是運作良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.87,0:04:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是到現在因為看到經濟問題這個新的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.38,0:04:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以一定是想來達成互補彼此弱點的協議吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.72,0:04:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是成熟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的資料讓我同步吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.66,0:04:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒什麼不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是說不要吵嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.63,0:04:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.79,0:04:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是很認真的對決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我閉上嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.56,0:04:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 連阿東都這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明還是新人 這樣不會太傲慢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.07,0:04:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算一直輸也不要怪到別人頭上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會全部贏回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.58,0:04:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不這樣就不好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.69,0:05:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梭哈再怎麼說也是機率的遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.26,0:05:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼都是齋藤先生贏呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從剛才開始也非常在意這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其以現在用的規則來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.00,0:05:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要先記住所有人的牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.17,0:05:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後從第一張和最後一張 預測對方手上的牌就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.24,0:05:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必然都是齋藤先生贏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道為什麼 最後都是齋藤先生拿走籌碼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.18,0:05:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只因為他很會唬人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快我就會撕掉他那張面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.02,0:05:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那叫做撲克臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.59,0:05:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要記住喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們辦不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.46,0:05:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起我經歷過的生死關頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梭哈只不過是小孩子的遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.53,0:05:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還真敢說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.43,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我承認你是一流的狙擊手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.77,0:05:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 那就算能拿來跟梭哈比 還是沒什麼說服力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.31,0:05:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾有一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.81,0:05:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟讓我打心底發抖的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.85,0:05:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一對一做狙擊對決的經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.68,0:05:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從來沒有像當時那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.99,0:06:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺得跟對手打心理戰很可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.73,0:06:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,體驗過那次對決以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.06,0:06:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普通傢伙心裏想的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一眼就能夠預測出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種話很難以置信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順便問一下\N那是什麼樣的對手呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想聽嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—想聽！想聽！—想聽！想聽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.08,0:06:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人都跟的話 我就說給你們聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不是想聽你的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是2020年夏天的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.83,0:06:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歐亞大陸上每天進行著毫無意義的消耗戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於我不喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.60,0:06:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本在奇妙的政治平衡夾縫中享受著歸罪於他人的鎖國狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.94,0:07:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我以傭兵的身份加入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.28,0:07:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟墨西哥臨時政權同一陣線的義勇軍「赤色之白」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.05,0:07:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且當時我的左眼還平安無事待在眼窩裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.53,0:07:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中東的石油和南美的毒品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有特權的地方經常都有紛爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在先前的核大戰中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.04,0:07:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分裂且疲憊不已的美帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.81,0:07:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始認真考慮借由消滅新大陸的毒品市場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抑制國家預算的無謂流失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在打倒墨西哥貪污政權的名義下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美帝煽動聯合國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.06,0:07:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派遣英日混編的聯合國軍到南美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.93,0:07:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先以迅速攻佔首都為理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按慣例進行地毯式轟炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來甚至為了肅清抵抗的游擊隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.84,0:08:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做出派機械化師團到蒙特雷的野蠻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轟炸之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.84,0:08:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的夥伴被聯合國軍的裝甲部隊全滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.21,0:08:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我則一直在尋找適當的投降機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在這時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.95,0:08:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,監聽敵方通信的終端機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我即將跟持有戰術核武器的特殊部隊接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.40,0:08:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今無法拿出輝煌戰果的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.47,0:08:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心想就做做薪水份內的工作 順便換取緊張感這個禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.34,0:08:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對膽敢帶來戰術核武器這種可怕東西的不法之徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.24,0:08:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真心想要給予他們來自神之視線的恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.65,0:09:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太過在意關於攻擊醫療機構和教會的批判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留下太多游擊隊可以潛伏的巢穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.80,0:09:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是應該有兩個小隊在殲滅殘黨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是這樣就太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.17,0:09:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基本上你們都太粗枝大葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.34,0:09:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們英國人是不是太過度信仰SAS的傳說呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約翰蘭搏嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.76,0:10:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.63,0:10:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.21,0:10:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有狙擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.97,0:10:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趴下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川 先假設是使用衛星的狙擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.88,0:10:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,侵入衛星找出敵人的所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.95,0:10:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.65,0:10:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大媽伍長 不要動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有使用衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,半徑1公里內有大範圍干擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能從干擾的發射源算出對方的位置嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.73,0:10:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經在做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.10,0:10:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身手很好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.90,0:10:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是老兵嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有時間說廢話還不給我去搜索敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是菜鳥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.97,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從哪一邊射過來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠確認嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.54,0:10:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會被敵人聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改成電子腦通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.81,0:10:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己用用看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會被雜音嚇一跳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.02,0:10:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.98,0:11:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太大意了 完全掌握不到敵人的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.36,0:11:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點救他的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.02,0:11:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 中士 怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老薑!我們全體掩護你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.73,0:11:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁這個空檔救出大媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白雪去幫忙老薑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.14,0:11:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偏心的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 日本的那幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們負責西側建築物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的人負責東側
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心 你會得救的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.79,0:11:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.89,0:11:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.09,0:11:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.79,0:11:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在西側的建築物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.50,0:11:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得讓他們暫時搞不清楚我在哪裏才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流點冷汗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.35,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20厘米嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等！停止射擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.89,0:12:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老薑從什麼方向被擊中的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.60,0:12:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.67,0:12:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼傻話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒看到剛剛車子被打翻嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.57,0:12:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人在東邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.90,0:12:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 被包圍的可能性很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川 干擾來自哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是大概估計 有3個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個是東邊的建築物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.28,0:12:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外兩個應該是教堂和醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得東邊是誘餌嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.85,0:12:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多半是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20厘米打過來之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.75,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干擾有一瞬間的中斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.79,0:12:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且背對太陽是基本概念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.73,0:12:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.59,0:12:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東邊是誘餌而且多半沒人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.36,0:12:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果被包圍了應該會開更多槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.63,0:12:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定對方只有狙擊手一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.53,0:12:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼能這麼肯定?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狀況這麼告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.80,0:13:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有一個提議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.04,0:13:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在繞過東邊的建築物 到那邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現建築物裏面沒人之後 我會給你信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.35,0:13:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後大家一起朝教堂和醫院攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.08,0:13:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁這個時候回收伍長和戰術核武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去那個的話我們將會進退兩難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.62,0:13:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 你和白雪兩個人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迂迴之後再會合嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們馬上會發現東邊沒人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.93,0:13:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這之前再減少一個人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.01,0:13:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大媽你不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.93,0:13:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很細心地只裝了一發子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.37,0:14:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能大意的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過敵人多半只有一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.81,0:14:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用人數優勢壓迫他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.94,0:14:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.54,0:14:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狙擊手在教堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.81,0:14:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一口氣攻下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 他說不定在醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為干擾曾經停止過一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.51,0:14:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算剔除無法認定有發射機的廢墟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能放掉醫院這條線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.49,0:14:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道那邊到這裏的直線距離有幾公尺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.99,0:14:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定在教堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.86,0:14:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何如此肯定?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.99,0:14:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙可是故意連GPS都不用 純粹以狙擊技術來攻擊我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.53,0:14:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果他是個熟知科裏奧利法則的高手 所有人都會被殺掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.53,0:14:35.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Coriolis Effect:因慣性和地球自轉作用對移動物體的影響導致的複雜系統\N一直被使用在現代狙擊技術之中\N由法國力學家科裏奧利在1835年提出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,選哪一邊不都可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.87,0:14:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.14,0:14:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在戰場上比起勇猛 慎重才是長命的秘訣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.04,0:14:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好看那個母猩猩怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.41,0:14:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的職業高手就是指她那樣的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母猩猩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.92,0:14:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.03,0:15:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泡菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.73,0:15:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.83,0:15:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人在醫院裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.37,0:15:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.84,0:15:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先把箱子收回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伍長已經太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 暫時先撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以在這種地方全滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.29,0:15:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼傻話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泡菜被幹掉了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.16,0:15:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要報仇 我要殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先撤退之後再回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要撤退也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.07,0:15:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論選哪一條路 我們都得跟狙擊手作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然無法通訊 我們也無法呼叫援軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.71,0:15:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.18,0:15:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們還有人數上的優勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.48,0:15:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的同伴也被打死了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 進攻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.29,0:16:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.26,0:16:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有發生恐慌 就馬上重新組織攻勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.96,0:16:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有個優秀的指揮官在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.90,0:16:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道決戰的時刻已經接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.11,0:16:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊張感一口氣提高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.91,0:16:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每一個細胞都感覺的到腎上腺素的分泌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.45,0:16:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰場上的殺戮並不知道誰殺了誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.08,0:16:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 其中有個唯一的例外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.65,0:16:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是狙擊手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.69,0:16:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狙擊行為本身從一開始就替你發出了名片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.13,0:16:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以只有狙擊手不會成為俘虜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為殺死夥伴和指揮官的仇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.93,0:16:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命中注定會被當場格殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.84,0:17:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無後座力炮擊中大樓之後 大量發射煙霧彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藏在煙霧裏面衝進大樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.95,0:17:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.99,0:17:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 你們掩護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟白雪衝進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.90,0:17:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能當掩護的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.33,0:17:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是很好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要想成她很信賴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.11,0:17:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給少校吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面那傢伙會想辦法解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.48,0:17:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.92,0:17:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還被叫作母猩猩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙是什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.89,0:17:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只知道她是戰鬥的天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.89,0:17:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們叫她少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.10,0:18:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只跟少校對峙短短不到一秒鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.21,0:18:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就馬上想像到這次對射的結果而全身發抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.21,0:18:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我身為狙擊手的經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.28,0:18:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想定各種狀況之後得到的結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.58,0:18:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會被幹掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.59,0:18:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從她把步槍槍拖抵在腰部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.65,0:18:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼睛一眨也不眨的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.66,0:18:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我馬上知道她是全身義體的義體人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.63,0:19:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且手上是全感應式的半自動步槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.10,0:19:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然長、中、短距離的射擊控制軟體全都有安裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.34,0:19:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我嘗試在想像當中對少校發射一發子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.69,0:19:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一發子彈被少校擊落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.69,0:19:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用手動栓式槍機的我想躲到柱子後面的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.69,0:19:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二發就會擊中我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管模擬幾次都是一樣的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是可是 再這樣下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 再這樣下去早晚會被幹掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.14,0:19:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拚命想要怎麼樣才能逆轉這個局勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後我注意到某樣東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.81,0:19:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是少校剛開始擊中的干擾裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.78,0:19:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校為何一開始不惜花3發子彈去破壞那個東西呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.05,0:19:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.96,0:20:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說她沒有安裝中距離的射擊控制軟體?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 一定是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.06,0:20:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她雖然擔任狙擊手這個位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.06,0:20:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻把全感應式的步槍改成短槍管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是為了中距離時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.57,0:20:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以拿來代替機槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼她要跟我在這裏對射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就需要控制軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.01,0:20:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.35,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正從衛星下載控制軟體嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.02,0:20:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要來得及啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙技術不差嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.04,0:20:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從現在起當我的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.87,0:20:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從一開始就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.15,0:20:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.35,0:20:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從一開始就被少校的撲克臉騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.48,0:21:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我沒有拒絕的權利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.19,0:21:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是少校下達的第一個命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.87,0:21:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我最後一張牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.54,0:21:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故事雖然有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.14,0:21:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過跟這場賭局無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我賭手上所有的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.38,0:21:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我也賭全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.48,0:21:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.22,0:21:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這次你無法靠唬人來贏得勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.12,0:21:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想要的是黑桃的同花大順吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.16,0:21:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 你什麼牌都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.00,0:21:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為黑桃A早就在我這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒有勝算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且剛剛的話也是騙人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.51,0:21:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故事雖然有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.24,0:21:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 我記得在以前某部電影看過類似的情節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.38,0:22:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 全部都是編的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.15,0:22:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.93,0:22:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天就玩到這裏為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.06,0:22:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東 記得算清楚喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.30,0:22:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺得不好意思了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.10,0:22:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 新人 先墊一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.34,0:22:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是任性的前輩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.44,0:22:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齋藤先生真的什麼都沒有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.71,0:22:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家快看快看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.95,0:22:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齋藤先生最後用黑桃九完成了同花順喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.25,0:22:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.16,0:22:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說剛剛的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.06,0:22:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.73,0:22:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.41,0:23:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.12,0:23:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.69,0:23:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.60,0:23:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的美麗事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.97,0:23:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.31,0:23:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.61,0:23:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字—然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.18,0:23:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我審視自身—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.15,0:23:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我—時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.45,0:23:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.82,0:23:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去讓這一切成真的—它就在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.83,0:24:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在軀殼裏的美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.97,0:24:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.20,0:24:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字—然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.84,0:24:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我審視自身—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.84,0:24:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我—時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.18,0:24:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.52,0:24:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去讓這一切成真的—它就在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.56,0:24:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在這個軀殼裏

